Package com.nitrous.gwt.earth.client.api.event

Interface Summary
BalloonListener Listen for balloon opening and closing events
FrameEndListener Listen for events that are fired when Earth has finished rendering the viewport.
KmlEventListener The generic event listener that can be registered by calling GoogleEarth.addEventListener
KmlLoadCallback A listener that can be notified when a KmlFeature has loaded.
MouseClickListener The interface that is implemented by a listener that wishes to be notified of mouse interactions with Google Earth.
MouseListener The interface that is implemented by a listener that wishes to be notified of mouse interactions with Google Earth.
MouseMoveListener The interface that is implemented by a listener that wishes to be notified of mouse interactions with Google Earth.
ViewChangeListener Listen for events that are fired when the view is changing in Earth.
